我由細細個聽到大<br />\n但就總係做唔到普及<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:39:18.000Z","msg":"以前係無技術得個吹字，宜家係真有可能，不過真係可以實用化都要等玖十幾年時間"},{"pid":"0773063d82329ca51aab078a749ebc230c676d79","tid":2300570,"uid":347528,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:42:26.000Z","msg":"唔理你有幾多隻眼 <br />\n只要激嬲我哋<br />\n我哋會插爆你隻眼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2dc2f84402ef96225df392e13e96c07dcae04f","tid":2300570,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"盲人終於有得用智能電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}